{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482659550,"sessionID":"ses_314328225ffewlGaXNfSOaaL0F","part":{"id":"prt_cebcdb88e001HVBLMsZSZKe7Ow","sessionID":"ses_314328225ffewlGaXNfSOaaL0F","messageID":"msg_cebcdb0c4001D3LIlGguwoiFZc","type":"text","text":"Now I have a clear picture. There's already a `token-collector.ts` and it's wired into `monitor.ts`. What's missing is:\n\n1. **Persistence** — writing UsageRecords to `.wombo-combo/usage.jsonl` (append-only JSONL)\n2. **Loading and aggregation** — `groupBy(field)`, `filterByDateRange(since, until)`, `totalUsage()`\n3. **Wiring the persistence into ProcessMonitor** so records are written as agents emit events\n\nLet me explore further to see if there's already a `token-usage.ts` file or any existing usage persistence code.","time":{"start":1773482659550,"end":1773482659550}}}
