{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482816210,"sessionID":"ses_314328225ffewlGaXNfSOaaL0F","part":{"id":"prt_cebd0067b00200kz3A6lrMCs6r","sessionID":"ses_314328225ffewlGaXNfSOaaL0F","messageID":"msg_cebcffcbd001A51hK4yY3zX8JU","type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### 1. `src/lib/token-usage.ts` — New module (294 lines)\n\n**Persistence layer:**\n- `appendUsageRecord(projectRoot, record)` — Appends a single `UsageRecord` as a JSON line to `.wombo-combo/usage.jsonl`. Creates the directory/file if needed.\n- `loadUsageRecords(projectRoot)` — Loads all records from the JSONL file, skipping malformed lines defensively.\n\n**Aggregation engine:**\n- `totalUsage(records)` — Computes aggregated totals (input_tokens, output_tokens, cache_read, cache_write, reasoning_tokens, total_tokens, total_cost, record_count) across a set of records.\n- `filterByDateRange(records, since?, until?)` — Filters records by ISO 8601 date range (inclusive on both ends, either bound optional).\n- `groupBy(records, field)` — Groups records by `task_id`, `quest_id`, `model`, `provider`, or `harness` and returns a `Map<string, UsageTotals>`.\n\n**High-level wrapper:**\n- `UsageStore` class — Wraps persistence + querying into a single object. Designed to plug directly into `TokenCollector`'s callback.\n\n### 2. `src/lib/monitor.ts` — Wiring changes\n\n- `ProcessMonitor` now creates a `UsageStore` alongside `TokenCollector` in its constructor\n- Every `UsageRecord` parsed from agent `step_finish` events is automatically persisted to `.wombo-combo/usage.jsonl`\n- Write failures are caught silently (non-critical — agent monitoring continues uninterrupted)\n- Re-exports `UsageStore`, `appendUsageRecord`, `loadUsageRecords`, `totalUsage`, `filterByDateRange`, `groupBy`, `UsageTotals`, and `GroupableField` from `monitor.ts` for convenience\n\n### Verification\n- `bun run typecheck` — passes cleanly\n- `bun run build` — passes cleanly (177 modules, 1.29 MB)","time":{"start":1773482816198,"end":1773482816198}}}
